It means

00:10:05.344 --> 00:10:08.448
Substantial to the highest degree.

00:10:09.568 --> 00:10:12.864
It's curious, isn't it? So we pray, give us grace.

00:10:13.056 --> 00:10:14.048
are

00:10:14.208 --> 00:10:17.056
Super substantial bread

00:10:19.168 --> 00:10:25.600
St. Jerome, when he was rendering this Greek text into Latin in the Vulgate, look it up. Go online, look it up.

00:10:25.472 --> 00:10:26.720
He says,

