Panem super substancialum.

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:34.240
That's exactly it. Our super substantial bread. Yeah.

00:10:35.168 --> 00:10:39.808
Now, a lot of reasons, you know, take me too far afield. Why we say daily, right?

00:10:39.648 --> 00:10:41.664
But the Greek is

00:10:41.664 --> 00:10:43.744
Super substantial.

00:10:44.416 --> 00:10:45.696
Okay

00:10:45.376 --> 00:10:47.520
What bread are we asking for?

00:10:47.264 --> 00:10:52.160
We're not just asking for the bread that will feed our bodies. That's the point.

00:10:52.256 --> 00:10:57.824
Give us each day this super substantial bread.

00:10:58.016 --> 00:11:00.256
we Catholics know what he's talking about

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:02.688
We talk about

00:11:02.528 --> 00:11:03.968
The Eucharistic

00:11:03.776 --> 00:11:04.960
Bread,

00:11:05.184 --> 00:11:06.368
being

00:11:06.368 --> 00:11:09.472
Trans substantiated

00:11:09.216 --> 00:11:11.456
into the body of Christ.

00:11:12.384 --> 00:11:14.176
Not ordinary bread,

00:11:13.952 --> 00:11:16.064
And that's just a symbol of Christ.

00:11:16.640 --> 00:11:17.920
Who cares?

00:11:18.336 --> 00:11:19.168
But,

00:11:19.136 --> 00:11:22.848
The super substantial bread

00:11:22.944 --> 00:11:24.032
That's it.

